snippet.title: Captain & Company - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Avast! Sneak peek of the next great pirate adventure game, Captain & Company! 🏴‍☠️

Set sail with friends in epic 128-player naval battles and pillage your way to becoming the wealthiest pirates on the high seas!

Climb aboard, landlubbers! ⛵ capnco.gg

Stay in the loop and join the adventure!

Join our discord: https://discord.gg/scbWQ9PDCQ
